Adds a per-pixel output ring buffer to gambatte's PPU.

Every pixel written to the framebuffer also pushes its 2-bit shade
index to a ring buffer in PPUPriv. External code drains the buffer
via pixelBuf()/pixelBufSize()/pixelBufClear() on the GB class.

